{"tid":1517664,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"呢四個中國女子接力隊成員之中，你覺得邊個最靚女？？","createTime":"2019-08-30T03:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T05:04:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c70c455e9fc3c7edd7fb86b891c82584971c7665","tid":1517664,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:45:51.000Z","msg":"中國女子接力隊成員遭質疑是男兒身！網友看到休閒照狂喊：也太帥&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3201599/org/529b678f505b5eb22a72f3cfcc74c9cd.jpg/epqGmJgNPzm116v-hiTfuk0oH_xkZpKLyWfBTslnwU4?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3201599%2Forg%2F529b678f505b5eb22a72f3cfcc74c9cd.jpg%2FepqGmJgNPzm116v-hiTfuk0oH_xkZpKLyWfBTslnwU4%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=7c3a4bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n閱讀下一篇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n單打喬有望重返NBA！五隊邀請試訓，有望加盟76人輔佐大帝衝冠&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n上個月底舉行的中國全國大學生田徑錦標賽，湖南女子接力隊一舉獲得女子4X100公尺接力賽金牌，但其中兩名跑手的身形、樣貌及聲音引起高度關注，遭懷疑是男兒身。<br />\n<br />\n惹起「性別疑雲」的兩名跑手，分別是廖夢雪及童曾歡，留短髮的兩人與隊友一起掛著金牌踏上頒獎台，眉宇間英氣十足、身形亦比其他女跑手更加有陽剛味，幾乎沒有曲線可言；賽後受訪時，聲線也像男性般低沉，有指稱兩人在賽後遭要求接受性別檢查。<br />\n<br />\n廖夢雪（右二）及童曾歡（右三）參加女子接力賽，遭懷疑是男兒身。（視覺中國）<br />\n&uarr;廖夢雪（右二）及童曾歡（右三）參加女子接力賽，遭懷疑是男兒身<br />\n<br />\n據中國傳媒報導，兩人的檢查結果「沒有問題，只是外表長得有點像男性」，更有媒體批評這種做法是「侮辱」。不過大陸網友則大多持不同意見，在《網易》的報導之下，較溫和的網友表示「雖然不太禮貌，但是這確實讓人難以相信兩位是女運動員」、「檢查是應該的，確保公平公正」；有比較毒舌的則說：「我以為是男女混合接力賽」、「用藥過度」、「最像男人了，這比中國男星鹿晗、徐蔡坤要有男人味的多」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而廖孟雪微博上的休閒照被PO出後，也被大批網友評論表示「也太帥了吧！」「比男生還帥！」"},{"pid":"699bd3a21152451cd881b9fbb74526fab589a003","tid":1517664,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8uSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=85965cb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8uSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=ec96091d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8uSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=1b96e4d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"bbc9a5895bfe671e0852e01592eae90c3e532d82","tid":1517664,"uid":270281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"明眼人都知中間2個有丁絲打黎"},{"pid":"f9b57f6bf00a71d2c31060717c171cba27871e89","tid":1517664,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:48:07.000Z","msg":"右二最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43aef5335d73e4757cdad64fbc4d2c5c2c726b48","tid":1517664,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"無知一問，閹割完嘅男人會仲係男人定已經變咗女人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80310ecb679000e7dfe1c45badb0e76ce277519","tid":1517664,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開係學術台做咩 神秘台就差唔多"},{"pid":"a301a916c916234f5c6a52749a44e018f7510aa5","tid":1517664,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:01:58.000Z","msg":"支那真係無奇不有"},{"pid":"f298026460499c